{"tid":125150,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"原來我係公司咁重要","createTime":"2017-02-18T08:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T12:40:44.000Z","uid":79484,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f28830d0df0d5ed62bc2c721b24abb3e49633fee","tid":125150,"uid":79484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:34:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我已經係公司做左2年，眾所周知我係最hea既一個，係呢方面我絕對冇對手。因為同行㴝講人工唔低，但工作量奇低。返工時間朝九晩七，所以我每日都準時9點起身，7點準時返屋企。而返工每日最大既煩惱就係睇咩劇同去邊度食妟。今日食妟唔知點解有同事講起最有價值同事呢個話題，佢地一致認定係我。原因係只要一日有我存在，而佢地冇重大過失，基本上都可以好平安。因為公司有咩事要郁人，一定係郁我先，我就成為左所以同事第一道防線。比佢地講一講，我都覺得自己有少少偉大，而呢個角色都容易carry<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e07c73df580b01d3137f03e73d7a9c2c50c23e8","tid":125150,"uid":79484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff2c50e7815aa9f2777f51ba545bd6815877e11","tid":125150,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:41:36.000Z","msg":"我都係呢種角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cff60fcf6c7295144a8f17cde8600980b4ff89","tid":125150,"uid":74751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"9點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bce91aacd035e38162d2e35fb5d4d6bd128def","tid":125150,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:45:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"899cc8dbeaf6a91a8645e7afa3f6272a8eeb2d29","tid":125150,"uid":79484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:47:24.000Z","msg":"而呢個角色都<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔</span>容易carry<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" clas